title: Saina Nehwal enters quarterfinals of French Open
text: Saina Nehwal enters quarterfinals of French Open Friday, 23 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) Saina Nehwal dished out a superb game to see off the World Championship bronze medallist Minatsu Mitani 21-19 21-16.
